				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: New Bard seeking help - Skills seem to have Stopped<a name="47448"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 21 04 9:15 PM</span></td>
