				<td colspan="2"><span>I originally did this but I need every hot button I can get my hands on. I use 8 buttons for songs (and there are currently 6 panels defined). I use two buttons for primary/secondaryt since  I am often changing intruments to get the greatest effect possible. This is most useful for AOE kiting (Brass and String) and Charm/DD (Wind and Drum).
<br />

<br />
I did tie the skills to macros I use for songs so that every time I cast a song I try for sense traps, and since I cast songs A LOT this works reasonable well.
<br />

<br />
By the way, before I get smaked for using song macros let me explain. My macros are a  simple /stopsong, /cast x. I find this to be much faster and more reliable than Alt-x twice (or once if previous failed!). It also allows me to easily switch to a more critical song if needed (like seleos!).
<br />

<br />
It appears I am at one of those SLOWWWWW spots, I will struggle though it. Thanks all for the advice and encouragement.</span></td>
