				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: New Bard seeking help - Skills seem to have Stopped<a name="47477"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 22 04 1:57 AM</span></td>
