				<td colspan="2"><span>I have increased my Dex/Agi and that seems to be helping. I was under the impression that CHA was the Bard's primary attribute. I now know I am very wrong!
<br />

<br />
I would now argue that Dex/Agi (or perhaps hit points if you tank a lot) are FAR more important than CHA in most cases. While I can see some situations where CHA is important (pulling in an advanced LDON for example) it seems that it is better to focus on the other attributes at least through level 50 or so.
<br />

<br />
Thanks all</span></td>
